Fig. 2B shows the predicted nucleation threshold pressures for PFP (1.6 MPa), PFH (2.4 MPa), and PFO (3.4 MPa) emulsions. The experimentally measured ADV thresholds were 1.3 ± 0.3, 2.2 ± 0.2 MPa, and 3.0 ± 0.4 MPa for PFP, PFH, and PFO emulsions, respectively, at 2.5 MHz [16,48]. Variation of the geometric factor (

